flowchart TD
  Start([Start]) --> Initiate[Ordering Department triggers allocation planning]
  Initiate --> LoopStart[Loop through each requested merchandise]
  LoopStart --> Fetch[Retrieve candidate sites and stock quantities]
  Fetch --> Filter[Filter out sites that cannot meet delivery date]
  Filter --> Rank[Rank remaining sites ship over air, larger stock, minimize sites]
  Rank --> Check{Total feasible stock >= requested qty?}
  Check -->|Yes| Split[Split quantity across ranked sites]
  Split --> GenLine[Generate allocation plan lines]
  GenLine --> Show[Display draft allocation plan]
  Show --> Confirm[Confirm and save allocation plan]
  Confirm --> End([End])
  
  Check -->|No| Error[Generate Insufficient Supply Error]
  Error --> ShowError[Display error message to user]
  ShowError --> End
